Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:18.36,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:29.82,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.75,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:47.88,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.81,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:08.70,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:20.59,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:26.43,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:36.23,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:29.82,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.75,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:47.88,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.81,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:08.70,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:20.59,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:26.43,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:36.23,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:46.32,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(100,110)}Ep. 12 - The Night in Adelaide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:52.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop resisting, Sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:56.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's dangerous, Lucy-May!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:57.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No! Sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:01:59.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She fell down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:03.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Lucy-May!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.01,0:02:12.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:13.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:15.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Grab on to me, here! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:19.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't, Kate! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:20.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Lucy-May!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:27.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:33.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Someone! Someone, please come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:37.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Someone, we need you\Nto come immediately here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:41.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think I just heard someone's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:43.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, I heard it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:44.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:46.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was in the direction of river.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:00.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Someone! Someone, please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:09.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May! I'm coming to you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:15.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Let go! I need to go save Lucy-May!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:39.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:41.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A... A native!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:47.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:49.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kidnapping Lucy! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:54.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:04.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let that child go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You! What were you planning to do with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:09.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't let her go this instant,\Nyou'll regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:13.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That child is {\i1}my{\i0} child!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:16.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let her go now or else!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:25.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what it seems, dad!\NThis man was actually saving Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Both me and our Sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:29.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:45.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Burigan barina. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:46.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:50.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! This goat will have a baby very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:09.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May, how in the world\Ndid you end up in this situation? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:13.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky and me were about to drown. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:15.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Which means, what that man did...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:26.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We were quick to misjudge him. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:27.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:32.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But that's quite the complexion he has.\NHe was like Heracles, this guy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:34.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who is Heracles?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't. A famous Englishman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:40.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What a nonsense.\NIt's the name of a Greek God.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked that man his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:46.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. After all,\Nyou kinda owe him your life now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:48.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:53.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Until I find out what his real name is,\NI'll just call him Mr. Heracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:59.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May, you're soaking wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:01.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You need to change clothes quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:03.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, they'll go dry in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:06.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? This goat seems to be shivering a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:08.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, you poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky, are you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:14.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May, instead of worrying for the goat,\Nyou should be more worried for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:16.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll catch a cold this way.\NGo and change quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:21.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I left Tob behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:22.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:26.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I left Tob all alone at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:27.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:33.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look after the rest with those two,\Nso you'd better go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:43.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well you two just gave us a handful more\Nof unnecessary trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:45.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't do a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was Lucy-May who nearly got herself drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:50.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But that was because Sticky nearly drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:52.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So I was just trying to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'm glad neither you\Nnor the goat drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:59.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's return quickly,\Nwith that goat in tow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:02.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Tob hasn't gone anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good if so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:08.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob! Tob!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:14.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to trouble you, but I'm gonna\Nhave to ask you to look on that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:15.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob! Tob!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:27.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you drunk enough water by now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, we're going ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:33.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still worried about Tob,\Nand Lucy needs to quickly change clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:34.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:35.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need to give birth to a baby soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:47.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Falling into a river\Nis not very responsible of you! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob! Tob!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob was here, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:01.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe in the shack...\NI mean... have you looked in the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:03.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:05.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What about Bernard?\NHave you tried looking together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:09.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I asked him to check\Nif the kid didn't go to your house, by any chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:16.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you found him, Bernard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:18.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't found anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:22.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't suppose\Nhe went to the river past us? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:26.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be. In that case, we or someone\Nwould've noticed him on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go try looking that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:33.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Truly, I'm so sorry for all the trouble, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:35.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Found him! Found!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:41.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:51.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.\NReally, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:09:00.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Taking an afternoon nap in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What about Tob?\NHe was here all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:11.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No. It seems, he embarked\Non an expedition to Mrs. Mac's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:23.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob must've thought\NMrs. Mac's house was ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:27.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly. He's a kind of child you can't take your eyes off,\Nlest he'll wander wherever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:32.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If I were Tob I probably also wouldn't believe\Nthat such a run-down shack could be ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:35.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara, I feel like I've heard\Nmore than enough of that grumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:38.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,For sure. Let's call it enough, Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:43.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, where is Lucy-May's change of clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? They're still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But in which of the crates?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:47.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:53.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I really don't need to change\Nfrom these clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:54.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:56.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not one bit cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I like {\i1}these{\i0} clothes especially!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:13.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can't you walk even a bit faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:21.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What now? We're almost home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's keep going, Sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:37.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky, you don't mean to tell me\Nyou're about to have a baby, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Then it must really be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:44.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't do it here!\NTry to walk a little more. At least to the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:47.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, getting to the tent would be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:50.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There, feel free to have your baby, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:57.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's too soon!\NYou can't have a baby yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:02.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be in trouble.\NCome on, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:05.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please believe me,\Nyou can't have a baby in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:08.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, Sticky?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:13.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, just a little more.\NA few more steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:16.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! N-no way! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:18.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't have baby yet! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:21.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Come on, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:26.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ah! No! Wait! You can't! No-no-no-no-no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:35.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, sorry for all the trouble. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:39.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, sis. Kids sure look sweet when sleeping. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:41.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You should hurry up\Nwith having your own kid, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:46.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That is my own wish as well. But as you know,\Nsuch things are only for our good Lord to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:49.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That must be so. Now, if you excuse me,\NI'll go get this child to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:55.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help you with that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:58.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but I can handle the rest of it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:11:59.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's having a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:01.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's having a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:05.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky is about to have a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:07.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She just lies there on the grass\Nand won't budge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:10.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel sorry for the baby if it gets born right there. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:15.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate! Sticky's is having a baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:20.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I also hadn't seen a goat\Ngiving birth ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:22.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May, mind you manners a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now go back inside\Nand put this on properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:29.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, Lucy-May, you're in nothing but your underwear!\NDon't you have any shame? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:30.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Mac will laugh at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:31.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:37.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, you're telling us you can't move the goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:37.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:41.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But our Sticky is heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:45.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That guy previously lifted her with just one hand.\NWhich means I can, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:48.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really just as strong, Mr. Bernard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:49.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So the goat is finally in labor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:08.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At such a haphazard time, we'll have\Nan additional trouble of looking after the baby goat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's something you could task Lucy-May with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:14.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, let's get to carrying our things\Ninside this tent and the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Clara, will you lend us a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:17.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,May I help, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:20.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Out of question, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:25.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's something we should do ourselves.\NYou've helped us with so many things already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:31.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, I'm going home now,\Nplease tell my brother so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:33.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, Mrs. Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We hope your husband recovers soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:37.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:38.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:42.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If we had a good doctor here to show my husband to,\Nhe'd get better in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:43.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:44.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:02.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father, Mr. Pettywell is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Took him quite a while. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:07.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's because he kept fighting\Nthe oxcart owners. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder which plot are they going to settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:13.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows. As long as it's somewhere\Naway from here, I'm not complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Popple!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is something wrong, Mrs. Jane?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We have another addition\Nto our neighborhood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, you know these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Pettywells.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:30.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look, they bought the plot\Nright in front of our house. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:35.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Our neighborhood gets filled one after another,\Nand I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:39.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you need to shout it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:47.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because right there, on that spot, Mr. Pettywell\Nwill be assembling our prefabricated home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:48.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well it's no longer ours, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:51.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We've decided on letting Mr. Pettywell have it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:52.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ironic, isn't it? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:55.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They ended up living so close to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to watch him assemble a house there,\Nwhile we live in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:06.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I already gave you a promise\Nnot to speak out about that house anymore. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I was so delighted\Nto have neighbors such as Macs... 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:12.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Pettywell settles over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Adelaide is supposed to be spacious...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:17.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even Adelaide is not spacious enough, Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:32.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bernard, hold her real tight.\NYou can't afford to drop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:34.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She's heavier than I thought,\Nthat's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:38.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she does,\Nshe's carrying a baby inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:41.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think she has no less than five of them in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:42.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say it's two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:46.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,With this weight, she might as well\Nhave all 10 in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, where do I lay it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:51.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, can we use one of this tent's corners for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:54.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it'll happen today, or tomorrow at latest,\NI guess we've no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:58.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bernard, careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:15:59.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:00.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Down you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:03.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:09.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. It really is about to give birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And how many babies will it have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:14.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. We won't know until she's out of labor,\Nwhich is probably will take until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see, tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:19.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky, you can do it, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, this here is a very\Nvaluable thing, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:34.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? And that looks like our\Nnew neighbors right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:38.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, is Mr. Pettywell living there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:40.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems to be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:45.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to have something\Nagainst that man, you little ladies. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I hate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:48.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:55.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Pettywell owns a large chunk\Nof Southern Australian land.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:57.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Together with a mine on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:17:00.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we managed to put it together\Nthat he is wealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:02.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:06.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Pettywell seems to be coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:11.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I shouldn't think\Nhe's coming to say anything good. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:15.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, is this your house here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:16.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:20.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize it back when you passed by me\Non the way, but a servant told me just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:25.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It must be fate that you and me ended up living so close,\Nyou could even say we're neighbors. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:26.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:29.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But more importantly,\Nthat's one shabby house you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:32.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But we never expected it\Nto be a palace in the first place. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:36.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to lament selling away\Nyour chance to live in a prefabricated home. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:39.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I never had that kind of thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:41.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?! Well, that's a great relief to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:46.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, seeing it assembled right before your eyes\Nwould probably deliver you a great heartache.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:52.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,While we're at it, although I understand\Nit may sound a bit presumptuous, 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:56.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be so kind as to assemble\Nthat prefabricated home over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:58.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:18:02.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you supposed to know\Nhow to assemble it better than anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:07.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look - before, you said you'd assemble it\Nin two weeks, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But I'll have to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:14.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,For the moment, I have more things to sort out\Nabout my own house than you can shake a stick at.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:17.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely cannot afford helping you\Nbuild your house as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:20.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I never said you'll do it for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:22.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot agree to this,\Nregardless of the pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:25.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously enough, assembling it\Nwith my stupid servants spells disaster. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should find a carpenter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:33.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There can't be any skilled carpenters here in Adelaide!\NIt's the same as with doctors - there are none.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:35.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,One way or another, I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:40.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, I haven't even started\Nsorting things our on this end yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:42.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please try to accept it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:45.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I will pay exactly as much as you ask for...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:46.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting to rain, Mr. Pettywell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:53.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,People! Hurry up to carry our things\Nto inside the house and the tent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:56.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? How can one be so arrogant?\NAh! It's wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:03.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:13.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm getting drenched again,\NI really didn't have to change, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:31.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, that's one fine rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:35.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, make a bit of room please. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:37.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'll spill my drink this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:40.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, it's been decided\Nthat I'm going to Adelaide tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.89,0:19:44.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you'll have to hang around here\Nfor two or three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Parker managed to find\Nanother oxcart for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:49.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Big enough to take on all this luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:52.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Which means, I'll have to ride it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:55.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if you'll be able to {\i1}ride{\i0} it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:58.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're going to Adelaide,\Nyou'd better be prepared for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:00.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You think I can walk for ten kilometers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:04.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're drinking way too much alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:08.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a doctor?\NYou should take better care of your own health.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:15.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alcohol is the only thing\Nkeeping my spirits high, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:17.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I feel terrible disappointment from seeing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:21.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You do? From just seeing me do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:25.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly from that.\NI haven't told anyone about it yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:28.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,but I hope to become a doctor myself, in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:30.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well. That's a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:34.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} a {\i1}doctor{\i0}, huh? Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:36.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural that you're surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:39.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Without any way to learn it,\Nwanting to become a doctor... 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:41.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:43.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be plenty of ways for you to learn soon. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:48.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But how come you decided\Nthat you want to be a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:51.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to help people who are in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:21:00.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But now I'm not sure whether or not\NI feel like becoming a doctor anymore. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:01.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:05.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After meeting you, I'm starting to think\Na doctor's work is terribly tedious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I just help it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.69,0:21:17.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, when we get to Adelaide,\Nstop drinking that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:21.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And give your undivided attention\Nto people suffering from illnesses! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:29.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I let slip something arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:31.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Ben...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:36.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,About that... I don't think\NI'll be able to quit drinking at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:40.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I could vow here\Nthat I'll be examining my patients seriously. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:41.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely vow to do just that, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.19,0:21:52.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's stopped raining.
Comment: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:58.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:32.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:32.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:35.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The natives are chanting songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:36.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You think Mr. Heracles is there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:40.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Such a man should definitely be the natives' leader. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.64,0:22:41.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:45.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The one I owe my life to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.58,0:22:47.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He sure was a big guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:52.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He probably didn't understand a word of it,\Nwhen we were saying our thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:56.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We could try to memorize the words\Nthat his people use, instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:22:58.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,True...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.51,0:23:00.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.91,0:23:03.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sleepy. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.49,0:23:06.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:15.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After some time, our first night in Adelaide\Nhad become soundless again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.69,0:23:19.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even if today was by all means\Na very turbulent day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.68,0:24:06.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad made a house for our goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.82,0:24:10.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At that moment, we hear our names\Ncalled out from afar...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.92,0:24:12.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just who might it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.70,0:24:15.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next time:\N"Ben Has Arrived!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.02,0:24:16.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
